                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18161204-21-defend177 t18161204-21-punish123"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
